    <item>
      <title>特朗普和莫迪誓言深化国防关系并促进贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-14/trump-and-modi-announce-defense-deals-trade-boost-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在白宫新闻发布会上表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪同意开始谈判以解决美国贸易逆差问题。特朗普表示，美国将增加“数十亿美元的军售”，包括采取措施最终向印度提供 F-35 战斗机。与此同时，莫迪设定了到 2030 年将双边贸易额翻一番至 5000 亿美元的目标。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-14/trump-and-modi-announce-defense-deals-trade-boost-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 01:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 为星际之门前景蒙上阴影，熊市围绕软银</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/bears-circle-softbank-as-deepseek-clouds-outlook-for-stargate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于希望借助人工智能热潮复苏推动软银集团股价重回历史高位的投资者来说，DeepSeek 是一个重大障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/bears-circle-softbank-as-deepseek-clouds-outlook-for-stargate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税承诺刺激避险需求，黄金价格接近纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/gold-holds-near-record-as-trump-tariff-pledges-fuel-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统下令对多个国家征收互惠关税，加剧了贸易和全球经济的不确定性之后，金价稳定在历史高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/gold-holds-near-record-as-trump-tariff-pledges-fuel-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强气旋将于周五袭击澳大利亚铁矿石枢纽</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/powerful-cyclone-set-to-hit-australia-s-iron-ore-hub-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚铁矿石出口中心正面临周五晚些时候登陆的大型热带气旋，皮尔巴拉地区的港口设施、矿山和基础设施将面临危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/powerful-cyclone-set-to-hit-australia-s-iron-ore-hub-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的互惠关税加剧贸易紧张局势，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着市场消化特朗普总统可能对美国贸易伙伴征收互惠关税的影响，油价趋于稳定。]]></description>
