    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PHMSA 称 Sunoco 宾夕法尼亚燃油泄漏已持续 16 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/sunoco-fuel-leak-in-pennsylvania-lasted-16-months-phmsa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据监管机构的初步调查，Sunoco LP 运营的一条管道发生航空燃油泄漏至少 16 个月，污染了宾夕法尼亚州的居民水井，并且该管道可能存在发生进一步事故的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/sunoco-fuel-leak-in-pennsylvania-lasted-16-months-phmsa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 23:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税时间表提振市场情绪，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周五上涨，因为市场对美国对等关税可能需要数周时间才能生效的迹象做出了积极反应，这增加了通过谈判降低关税惩罚性程度的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 22:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产汽车股价上涨，本田退出为其他收购者打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/honda-nissan-parting-leaves-both-with-unresolved-problems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司股价周五上涨，因与本田汽车公司谈判的正式结束为包括鸿海精密工业股份有限公司和私募股权巨头 KKR &amp; Co. 在内的其他潜在收购者打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/honda-nissan-parting-leaves-both-with-unresolved-problems</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 11:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡考虑采取税收优惠措施以振兴股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由新加坡政府牵头的评估小组提出了重振股市的激励措施，这是在流动性低、新股上市稀缺的市场中采取的第一步措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/singapore-moots-tax-incentives-to-revive-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
